Name: 1858 by Caymus Vineyards Cabernet Sauvignon Paso Robles
Product_Highlights: Paso Robles, CA- From Caymus Vineyards. Black cherry and plum hit the front of the palate. Baking spice, with touches of vanilla and oak accompany the fruit while adding layers of complexity.

Name: Kendall-Jackson Vintner's Reserve Chardonnay
Product_Highlights: Rich and complex with notes of green apple, pear, and vanilla. Aged in French oak barrels for creamy texture.
